da, Ourense|Maceda]]\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Madanela]]\n|\n|[[Ladra (river)|Ladra]]\n|[[Vilalba]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Magros]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Mainzoso]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Regato da Mallada de Barbeir\u00f3n]]\n|\n|[[San L\u00e1zaro (river)|San L\u00e1zaro]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Mandeo]]\n|\n|\n|[[Sobrado, Galicia|Sobrado]], [[Curtis]], [[Aranga]], [[Irixoa]], [[Coir\u00f3s]], [[Paderne, A Coru\u00f1a|Paderne]], [[Betanzos]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mao, r\u00edo Cabe|Mao]]\n|[[O Mao, O Incio]]\n|[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]]\n|[[O Incio]], [[B\u00f3veda]], [[Monforte de Lemos]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Mao, r\u00edo Sil|Mao]]\n|[[Serra de San Mamede]]\n|[[Sil (river)|Sil]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Mao, r\u00edo Salas|Mao]]\n|[[Mu\u00ed\u00f1os]]\n|[[Salas (river)|Salas]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Marcel\u00edn]]\n|[[Vilardev\u00f3s]]\n|[[Arzo\u00e1]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Mariaqueira]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mariz (river)|Mariz]]\n|\n|[[Boedo, r\u00edo Parga|Boedo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Maro\u00f1a]]\n|\n|[[Xallas]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mart\u00edn (Galician river)|Mart\u00edn]]\n|[[Fonsagrada]]\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Masma]]\n|[[Serra do Xistral]], [[O Valadouro]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Foz]]\n|[[Abad\u00edn]], [[Alfoz]], [[Mondo\u00f1edo]], [[Lourenz\u00e1]], [[Barreiros, Lugo|Barreiros]], [[Foz]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Mazaricos (river)|Mazaricos]]\n|\n|[[Xallas]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Medo (river)|Medo]]\n|\n|[[Parga (river)|Parga]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Mendo (river)|Mendo]]\n|Curtis\n|[[R\u00eda de Betanzos]]\n|Curtis, [[Oza-Cesuras]], [[Coir\u00f3s]], [[Betanzos]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mente]]\n|[[Serra de Texeiras]]\n|[[Rabazal]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Mera, r\u00eda de Ortigueira|Mera]]\n|[[Alto do Caxado]], [[Serra da Faladoira]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Ortigueira]]\n|[[As Somozas|Somozas]], [[Ortigueira]], [[Cerdido]], [[As Pontes de Garc\u00eda Rodr\u00edguez]] \n|\n|-\n|[[Mera, r\u00edo Tambre|Mera]]\n|[[Calvos de Sobrecami\u00f1o, Arz\u00faa]]\n|[[Tambre (river)|Tambre]]\n|[[Arz\u00faa]], [[O Pino]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mera, r\u00edo Mi\u00f1o|Mera]]\n|[[Santalla de B\u00f3veda de Mera, Lugo]]\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[Lugo]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Mera, r\u00edo Mera|Mera]]\n|[[Bacur\u00edn, Lugo]]\n|[[Mera, r\u00edo Mi\u00f1o|Mera]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Mero (Galician river)|Mero]]\n|[[Montes da Tieira]]\n|[[R\u00eda do Burgo]]\n|[[Oza-Cesuras]], [[Abegondo]], [[Bergondo]], [[Cambre]], [[Culleredo]], [[Oleiros, Galicia|Oleiros]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[das Mestas]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[Serra de Meira]], [[Meira]]\n|[[Atlantic Ocean]]\n|[[R\u00e1bade]], [[Portomar\u00edn]], [[Ribadavia]], [[Melga\u00e7o Municipality, Portugal|Melga\u00e7o]], [[Mon\u00e7\u00e3o]], [[Tui, Galicia|Tui]], [[Valen\u00e7a do Minho]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]], [[Ourense (province)|Ourense]] e [[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Mi\u00f1or]]\n|[[Serra do Gali\u00f1eiro]], [[Gondomar, Pontevedra|Gondomar]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Vigo]]\n|[[Gondomar, Pontevedra|Gondomar]], [[Nigr\u00e1n]], [[Baiona, Pontevedra|Baiona]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Mi\u00f1oto]]\n|\n|[[dos Gafos]]\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Mi\u00f1otos]]\n|\n|[[Landrove]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rego Mollop\u00e1n]]\n|\n|[[Mandeo]]\n|[[Aranga]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Mondariz (river)|Mondariz]]\n|\n|