ru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Lexoso]]\n|\n|[[Grande, r\u00eda de Ribadeo|Grande]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Limia (river)|Limia]]\n|\n|[[Atlantic Ocean]]\n|[[Xinzo de Limia]], [[Ponte de Lima]], [[Viana do Castelo Municipality|Viana do Castelo]]\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]] e [[Portugal]]\n|-\n|[[Li\u00f1ares]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Li\u00f1eiras]]\n|\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Loba (river)|Loba]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Lodeiro (river)|Lodeiro]]\n|\n|[[Dubra (river)|Dubra]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Loio]]\n|\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Loira, Galiza|Loira]]\n|\n|[[Atlantic Ocean]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Lonia (river)|Lonia]]\n|[[Lo\u00f1a do Monte, Nogueira de Ramu\u00edn]]\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[Nogueira de Ramu\u00edn]], [[Pereiro de Aguiar]], [[Ourense]]\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Lor (river)|Lor]]\n|[[Pedrafita do Cebreiro]]\n|[[Sil (river)|Sil]]\n|[[Pedrafita do Cebreiro]], [[Quiroga, Galicia|Quiroga]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Lourenz\u00e1 (river)|Lourenz\u00e1]]\n|[[Serra de Lourenz\u00e1]]\n|[[Masma]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Lourido]]\n|\n|[[Anll\u00f3ns]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Louro]]\n|[[Pazos de Borb\u00e9n]]\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[Pazos de Borb\u00e9n]], [[Mos, Spain|Mos]], [[Redondela]], [[O Porri\u00f1o]], [[Tui, Galicia|Tui]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[L\u00f3uzara]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n===M===\n\n[[File:Sarria 0018.jpg|right|thumb|The Minho, Portomar\u00edn in the 1920s]]\n{| style = align=\"left\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"bonita\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 1em; padding: 0.5em; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-s