lla (river)|Ulla]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Ribadil]]\n|\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Ribeira Grande (river)|Ribeira Grande]]\n|[[Serra de Queixa]]\n|[[Camba (river)|Camba]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Ribeira Pequena]]\n|[[Serra de Queixa]]\n|[[Camba (river)|Camba]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Riodolas]]\n|\n|[[Casoio]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Regato de Rioseco]]\n|[[Monforte de Lemos]]\n|[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[de Riotorto]]\n|\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rego Riveiro]]\n|\n|[[Ulla (river)|Ulla]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Robra (river)|Robra]]\n|\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Roca (river)|Roca]]\n|[[Os Vilares, Guitiriz]]\n|[[Parga (river)|Parga]]\n|[[Guitiriz]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Regueiro de Rocaboa]]\n|\n|[[Sold\u00f3n]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rodeiro (river)|Rodeiro]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Rodil River|Rodil]]\n|[[Vilardongo]]\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rod\u00eds]]\n|\n|[[Calvar]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Rons (river)|Rons]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Rosende (river)|Rosende]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Rub\u00edn, r\u00edo Saa|Rub\u00edn]]\n|[[A Pobra do Broll\u00f3n]]\n|[[Saa (river)|Saa]]\n|[[A Pobra do Broll\u00f3n]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rub\u00edn, r\u00edo B\u00fabal|Rub\u00edn ou Albarellos]]\n|\n|[[B\u00fabal, r\u00edo T\u00e1mega|B\u00fabal]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Ruxida de Curveiros]]\n|\n|[[Boedo, r\u00edo Parga|Boedo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Ruzos]]\n|\n|[[Masma]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n===S===\n\n[[File:Ribeira Sacra. R\u00edo Sil. Lugo. Galiza.jpg|right|th