 Tenorio]], [[Cotobade]]\n|[[L\u00e9rez, r\u00eda de Pontevedra|L\u00e9rez]]\n|[[Cotobade]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Termes (river)|Termes]]\n|[[Empiade, Cerdeira, As Neves]]\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[As Neves]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Tines (river)|Tines]]\n|[[Mazaricos]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Muros e Noia]]\n|[[Mazaricos]], [[Outes]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Tolda]]\n|\n|[[Boedo, r\u00edo Parga|Boedo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Torneiros]]\n|\n|[[Az\u00famara]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Toxa]]\n|[[Forcarei]]\n|[[O Deza]]\n|[[Forcarei]], [[Silleda]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Traba (river)|Traba]]\n|[[Lousame]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Muros e Noia]]\n|[[Lousame]], [[Noia]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Trabada (river)|Trabada]]\n|\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Regato Trasadehesa]]\n|\n|[[Antiga]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Tras da Serra]]\n|[[Alto de San Xo\u00e1n]], [[Ribeira, Ambosores]]\n|[[Sor Ma\u00f1\u00f3n|Sor]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Rego de Tras das Penas]]\n|[[San Pedro do Incio, O Incio]]\n|[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Trimaz]]\n|\n|[[Ladra (river)|Ladra]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Tronceda]]\n|[[Serra do Xistral]]\n|[[Masma]]\n|[[Mondo\u00f1edo]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Tu\u00f1o]]\n|\n|[[Arnoia]]\n|\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Tur\u00eda (river)|Tur\u00eda]]\n|\n|[[Eo (river)|Eo]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n===U===\n\n{| style = align=\"left\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"bonita\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 1em; padding: 0.5em; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!width=\"125\"|Name\n!width=\"150\"|Source\n!width=\"150\"|Outlet\n!width=\"250\"|Flows through\n