ontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Carrozo do Val Herboso]]\n|\n|[[Sold\u00f3n]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vali\u00f1adares]]\n|\n|[[Masma]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vali\u00f1as]]\n|[[A Laracha]]\n|[[Mero (Galician river)|Mero]]\n|[[A Laracha]], [[Culleredo]], [[Cambre]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Valouta]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vao, r\u00edo Anll\u00f3ns|Vao]]\n|\n|[[Anll\u00f3ns]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Vao, r\u00edo Calvar|Vao]]\n|\n|[[Calvar]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[da Veiga]]\n|[[Monforte de Lemos]]\n|[[Cinsa]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Regato da Veiga]]\n|[[Monforte de Lemos]]\n|[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vent\u00edn]]\n|\n|[[Oitav\u00e9n]]\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Verdugo River|Verdugo]]\n|[[Outeiro Grande]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Vigo]]\n|[[A Lama]], [[Ponte Caldelas]], [[Soutomaior]], [[Pontevedra]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Vexo]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Vilacoba]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Vilacampa]]\n|\n|[[Landrove]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vilach\u00e1n]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Vilaflores]]\n|\n|[[Parga (river)|Parga]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vilamaior]]\n|\n|[[Xallas]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Vilar (river)|Vilar]]\n|\n|[[Xallas]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Rego do Vilar]]\n|\n|[[Pequeno (river)|Pequeno]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vilari\u00f1o (river)|Vilari\u00f1o]]\n|\n|[[Arnego]]\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[de Vilarmiel]]\n|\n|[[Sold\u00f3n]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[de Vilasel\u00e1n]]\n|[[Ribadeo]]\n|\n|[[Ribadeo]]\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[de Vilaver]]\n|\n|[[Ser (river)|Ser]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Vixoi]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n===X===\n\n{| style = align=\"left\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"bonita\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 1em; padding: 0.5em; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!width=\"125\"|Name\n!width=\"150\"|Source\n!width=\"150\"|Outlet\n!width=\"250\"|Flows through\n!width=\"75\"|Province\n|-\n|[[Xallas (river)|Xallas]]\n|monte Castelo, [[Coristanco]]\n|[[Atlantic Ocean]]\n|[[Coristanco]], [[Santa Comba, Galicia|Santa Comba]], [[A Ba\u00f1a]], [[Zas]], [[Mazaricos]], [[Carnota]], [[Dumbr\u00eda]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Xanceda]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Xantas]]\n|\n|[[Sor Ma\u00f1\u00f3n|Sor]]\n|\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Xares]]\n|[[Pena Trevinca]], [[A Veiga]]\n|[[Bibei]]\n|[[A Veiga]], [[O Bolo]], [[Larouco]]\n|[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]]\n|-\n|[[Xar\u00edo]]\n|[[Ar, Vilar, Pontedeume|Ar]], [[Pontedeume]]\n|[[Baxoi (river)|Baxoi]]\n|[[Pontedeume]], [[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[da Xesta]]\n|\n|[[Oitav\u00e9n]]\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Xesta]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n|[[Xoanceda]]\n|\n|\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Xora]]\n|\n|\n|[[Vimianzo]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Xunco]]\n|[[Montes de Cabaleiros]]\n|[[Bay of Biscay]]\n|\n|[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]]\n|-\n|[[Grande de Xuvia|Xubia]]\n|[[Montes da Serra]], [[Somozas, Galicia]]\n|[[R\u00eda de Ferrol]]\n|[[Somozas, Galicia]], [[Nar\u00f3n]], [[Neda, Galicia|Neda]]\n|[[La Coru\u00f1a (province)|A Coru\u00f1a]]\n|-\n|[[Xuliana]]\n|[[Taboexa, As Neves]]\n|[[Minho (river)|Minho]]\n|[[As Neves]]\n|[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n=